rules.name: Open and inclusive
rules.description: This community is open to *anyone* to talk about Apple or *anything* having to do with Apple or technology. Respect that and respect everyone in the community.

rules.name: No RTing community Tweets back to the Community
rules.description: Do not RT community Tweets back to the community w/o mod permission. You can: 1) RT community tweets out of the community 2) RT outside Tweets to the community.

rules.name: Promotion
rules.description: Any promotion must be approved by a mod. You can share your Tweets and relevant outside links. Unless approved, no promoting communities and no affiliate links.

rules.name: English only
rules.description: Only Tweet/post in English in this Community. Exceptions are for Apple or other branded content that is *only* in another language and for known-user replies.

rules.name: Keep tweets/replies on topic & No Spam
rules.description: Tweets and replies should be able to refer to Apple or technology in some shape or form. This includes no spam. Spam's definition is up to the mod's discretion.
